summary: This is an email chain from December 2020 discussing the location of digitized VHS tapes containing interviews with Epstein victims. The correspondence seeks to confirm the location of these files and verify transfers from the previous summer, specifically to determine if a video relating to a named victim exists.

events.title: Inquiry about Epstein victim interview tapes
events.description: An email is sent inquiring about the location of digitized VHS tapes of interviews with Epstein victims, specifically to determine if a video relating to a named victim exists.

events.title: Confirmation of transfers
events.description: A reply confirms that certain transfers from the previous summer are the ones in question.

events.title: Forwarding of email chain
events.description: The email chain discussing the victim interview tapes and transfers is forwarded.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain from December 2020 discussing digitized VHS tapes of interviews with Epstein victims.
The correspondence seeks to locate these files to determine if a video relating to a specific named victim exists.
References are made to transfers of these materials that occurred in the summer of 2019 or 2020.
The email chain involves multiple parties, but all personal names and email addresses are redacted in the provided text.
The document indicates ongoing efforts to manage and locate evidence related to Epstein victims.
